{"tid":601853,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【科網股】騰訊大股東出售1.9億騰訊股份","createTime":"2018-03-22T14:06:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-22T14:53:59.000Z","uid":64863,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0588936a1b61ce2e5bbf8dd89e83f5eecc97ee23","tid":601853,"uid":64863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T14:06:31.000Z","msg":"Who the _ is Nasper?<br />\n<br />\n這應該是騰訊投資者今天心底裡的問題，<span style=\"color: red;\">因為Nasper決定要出售800億規模的騰訊股票</span>。騰訊在消息前今天已跌了5%。<br />\n<br />\nNaspers是誰？<br />\n<br />\n是最長情的騰訊股東。<br />\n馬化騰本人時不時在減持，從上市時的14.43%，減持至少於9%。但Naspers從未心旌搖蕩，Naspers曾在其官方文件中驕傲的宣稱，從買入騰訊開始，它只拿分紅，從來沒有賣出過一股騰訊股票。<br />\n<br />\n總部位於南非開普敦的Naspers創立於1915年，起初只是一間出版商，1994年在約翰內斯堡交易所上市。但佢做咩唔重要，因為最成功的決定只要一個：<br />\n<br />\n「2001年5月投資騰訊3200萬美元」<br />\n買入價是$4，當時騰訊還未柝細。回報超過1000%。<br />\n<br />\n長情大股東減持，散戶擔心，基金磨牙。<br />\n但有班人一定好開心：做個deal既ibanker<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/220050_cbc3784228aaff5d9c7a679e793801f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F220050_cbc3784228aaff5d9c7a679e793801f5.jpg&h=5e2ae52f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nowwwhatapp/photos/a.1808416246066479.1073741829.1805981482976622/1899334090308027/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnowwwhatapp%2Fphotos%2Fa.1808416246066479.1073741829.1805981482976622%2F1899334090308027%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=vmp%2BLbkGsXc7YfaF1kid1CwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=44769f12\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/nowwwhatapp/photos/a.1808416246066479.1073741829.1805981482976622/1899334090308027/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n早知入隻熊仔啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91864416a19c58b18b31d811504419e2b898193e","tid":601853,"uid":64863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T14:09:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0f282869ce34b31ae8ff68f653720f789a91ef2","tid":601853,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T14:10:50.000Z","msg":"科網股爆破"},{"pid":"83cab82184ce67bf4b88bae22ed40efa040927c9","tid":601853,"uid":52942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T14:11:10.000Z","msg":"they know war is coming"},{"pid":"17d94f977397c5cea57e706ed6e3780b88fba875","tid":601853,"uid":126648,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T14:12:21.000Z","msg":"點解"},{"pid":"c6c7186786275542e80b177b168d50a4dba629bf","tid":601853,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17d94f977397c5cea57e706ed6e3780b88fba875","tid":601853,"uid":126648,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T14:12:21.000Z","msg":"點解"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T14:14:33.000Z","msg":"賺夠"},{"pid":"b72e74c71c14da2ae786b4c8d7009de68ec2dbc4","tid":601853,"uid":64863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T14:16:57.000Z","msg":"岩岩入左手你先黎單咁既deal，真係屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2be40348acc6eedd2a8b8b62741a74957bd4721b","tid":601853,"uid":63944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T14:19:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9e32f2ea93899c66439784bd52b4b53e7d639134","tid":601853,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T14:25:13.000Z","msg":"騰訊（0700）大股東Naspers全球配售1.9億股份，市場消息指，有關股份已全數獲認購，大部分接貨者為對沖基金，配股價折讓區間介乎6%至9%，相關配售計劃將今明日凌晨1時結束。<br />\n<br />\nNaspers宣布沽貨，貨值超逾800億元，但銷售文件未有提配售作價，僅稱參考今日收市價，在配售結束前始定價。市場流傳，基金界現時普遍開價是較收市價折讓5%，按騰訊今日收報439.4元計，即約417.4元。<br />\n<br />\n據銷售文件顯示，騰訊大股東南非Naspers計劃減持最多1.9億股，以今日收市價計，相當於835億元，完成後持股量由33.2%降至31.2%。"},{"pid":"c4294bca369b1f244ce426bf0446cf3271e38759","tid":601853,"uid":25884,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T14:27:45.000Z","msg":"最開心係啲ibanker, 訓係到收fee. 今鋪肥過肥仔水"},{"pid":"8cfc9d6d0ef2d405c84945cb5fc0ea380a769161","tid":601853,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T14:29:45.000Z","msg":"對沖基金如果買到，夠玩700過世，舞上舞落任佢玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cec312f3330ddbfea27a5047d512f4f3a79b47c","tid":601853,"uid":64863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T14:53:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}